title: 3BD /2BA HOME IN SAGE BAY, READY FOR YOU!
posting_body: ['Lovingly maintained three-bedroom home with an expansive living room and patio set in the serene community of Sage Bay!', 'This adorable bungalow features a well-distributed layout with an abundance of natural light throughout, with accordion shutters installed for extra protection for an added layer of protection!', 'Living room showcases an elegant accent wall and huge glass panels that open to your spacious covered patio.', 'Adjacent to the living room is the kitchen furnished with a full range, vented hood, microwave, dishwasher, and a French-door fridge.', 'Countertops offer plenty of space, and cabinets provide lots of storage for your cooking gadgets and dinnerware!', 'Primary bedroom can easily fit a Queen-sized bed, and has an ensuite full bath with walk-in shower.', 'There’s another full bath with a shower and-tub combo shared by two moderately-sized secondary bedrooms.', 'Other utilities include in-unit laundry, water heater, and parking for three cars.', 'Property is pet-friendly, so you can enjoy the place with your furbabies!', 'Located in the quiet and safe neighborhood of Saga Bay, where residents enjoy its family-oriented atmosphere, sandy lakefront beaches, beautiful parks, and other amenities such as tennis courts, baseball field, fitness gyms, walking paths, picnic areas, and water sport activities such as kayaking and paddle boarding!', 'Lease Term: 12 months', "Deposit Amount: One month's rent", 'Pet Deposit: $500', 'Included In Rent:', 'Trash', 'Landscaping', 'Parking', 'HOME ID: 7362ac7fa318ff70']
